description: Discover unparalleled luxury and functionality in this exquisite 2021 new construction residence, ideally positioned at the heart of South Boston's coveted East Side. Boasting a generous floor plan spread across three levels, this 2 bed/2.5 bath meticulously crafted home presents a sophisticated blend of modern amenities and timeless elegance. A substantial bonus den, provides an ideal space for remote work or media room or gym. With 2.5 meticulously appointed baths, including an en-suite master bath. The culinary enthusiast will delight in the sleek and modern all-white kitchen, complete with Bosch appliances, white shaker-style cabinets, and a striking Michelangelo white veined quartz waterfall island accented with luxurious gold finishes. Additionally, residents will appreciate the convenience of private storage, enhancing the ease of everyday living. Experience the epitome of urban convenience with a prime location that offers effortless access to an array of amenities.
